          "label": "Insulated Cladding Panels",
          "defaultOn": true,
          "text": "The Supplier shall supply insulated cladding panels for {{app}}:\n\nType: {{panelType}}\nThickness: min {{thk}} mm, width: {{width}} mm\nCore: {{core}}, fire: min {{fire}}\n\nExterior: {{extSh}} mm, {{extCoat}}, {{extCol}}, {{extProf}}\nInterior: {{intSh}} mm, {{intCoat}}, {{intCol}}, {{intProf}}\n\nFixing: {{fixing}}\nArea: {{area}} m²\nHeights: {{heights}}\nMax length: {{maxLen}} m\n\nConfirm: type, U-value, fire class, DoP/CE, max length, weight/m².\nSTM reserves the right to reject non-compliant alternatives.",
